data.description: Stunning Marsh Creek Rare Custom single story home has Owned Solar, 4 bedrooms, 2 1/2 baths over 2,500 s.f., 3 car garage, Inground swimming pool and spa, Pool house changing bath, Gorgeous landscaping, Formal living and dining rooms, Family room with cozy brick fireplace, culinary kitchen with double ovens, cooktop, microwave, granite countertops, Walk in Pantry and Pull out cabinet shelves, fabulous tile and wood flooring, Grand master suite with wonderful master bath, shower stall and soaking tub, walk in closet, Water filtration system, water softener, intercom system, plumbed for central vac, possible RV parking all on over 1/4 acre lot and Beautifully landscaped!   This home is move in ready and waiting for it's new owner to Love it as much as the owners do!
